{"tid":1165760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：分享採訪八九民運經歷 夫子導賞六四館 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-05-22T04:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T04:15:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1ca4e1560a7638b74822b13c5253756d356df0","tid":1165760,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190522/20684457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F20684457&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=8d458c2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F20684457&h=fd1d59a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190522/20684457</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：分享採訪八九民運經歷<br />\n夫子導賞六四館 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190522/large/a0805a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190522%2Flarge%2Fa0805a.jpg&h=74a333e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六四紀念館上月底正式重開。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n幾經波折，支聯會終於喺旺角重開「六四紀念館」，令到市民有更多機會認識六四史實。不過淨係睇未必夠深入，如果有人為參觀市民即場解說，肯定別有一番體會。支聯會亦特別就此搞搞新意思，搵嚟香港《文匯報》前駐京辦主任、人稱「夫子」嘅劉銳紹負責帶領導覽團，夫子當年有份深入採訪八九民運，佢會以當年嘅親身經歷，為大家導覽六四紀念館中各項展品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190522/large/a0805b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190522%2Flarge%2Fa0805b.jpg&h=fa2c3402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個導覽團會喺本周六（25日）下午5點至6點舉行，地點當然係位於旺角道藝旺商業大廈10字樓嘅六四紀念館。名額得20個，先到先得，如果想報名或者查詢，可致電2459 6489、或電郵至64museum@alliance.org.hk，網上報名亦可。 <br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：勇武美少女躋身眾志常委 (李八方)"}]}